## [{{ version }}]
### Added
- ci: use per-MR Docker image tag mr-${CI_MERGE_REQUEST_IID} to prevent cross-MR image overwrites

### Changed
- rules.yml: Remove obsolete merge request cases
- yocto: add pigz tool
- Add TQEM_APT_UBUNTU_SOURCES variable to provide a custom DEB822-formatted apt sources file at
  build time. Without the variable the base image apt configuration is used unchanged.
- Update base image from Ubuntu 22.04 to Ubuntu 24.04
- docker.Dockerfile: replace cruizba/ubuntu-dind with Ubuntu 24.04 and official Docker CLI
- yocto.Dockerfile: replace libsdl1.2-dev with libsdl2-dev and libegl1-mesa with libegl-dev
- ubuntu.Dockerfile: remove default Ubuntu 24.04 ubuntu user before creating tqemci
